  "detailed_description": "Introduction<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJo is an extremely talented designer, who works for a company run by Mr. Charles all the year round. His works are also loved by people in the city. However, after a period of anxiousness and fretfulness, he finds that the inspiration of his creation is gradually fading. Should he take some time off, leave the city for a while, or see a therapist? Perhaps it will happen more than Joe  expects, that will open up a huge conspiracy planned in the past.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n“Dear Ashely” will show you a fantastic personal growth journey through the memory of the past.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAn ordinary dream “Even if abandoned by the whole world, at least I have you.” <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA huge conspiracy “ No matter how much time and cost I will spend, I'll wake you up.”<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeature<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA game with very simple mode of operation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRich game plots that are the game player following Jo to explore the past.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHaving different styles of maps for players to play.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA horrible, premeditated conspiracy will be found.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe normal flow of the game is about an hour and a half, including five different-meaning endings.",
  "about_the_game": "Introduction<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJo is an extremely talented designer, who works for a company run by Mr. Charles all the year round. His works are also loved by people in the city. However, after a period of anxiousness and fretfulness, he finds that the inspiration of his creation is gradually fading. Should he take some time off, leave the city for a while, or see a therapist? Perhaps it will happen more than Joe  expects, that will open up a huge conspiracy planned in the past.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n“Dear Ashely” will show you a fantastic personal growth journey through the memory of the past.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAn ordinary dream “Even if abandoned by the whole world, at least I have you.” <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA huge conspiracy “ No matter how much time and cost I will spend, I'll wake you up.”<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeature<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA game with very simple mode of operation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRich game plots that are the game player following Jo to explore the past.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHaving different styles of maps for players to play.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA horrible, premeditated conspiracy will be found.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe normal flow of the game is about an hour and a half, including five different-meaning endings.",
